ient": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775013677}, {"pid": 863075126, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 24, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 11:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863074685,45974302,3244]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67142257]兰斯洛t[/uid] (2026-04-01 11:20):[/b]<br/><br/>黄白交织缩量一起去摸电门了，下午剧情肯定很吓人…<br/>我既希望增量资金入场突破3955，又害怕他真的起来了把我给甩下车了[s:a2:大哭][s:a2:大哭][s:a2:大哭]，又不愿意他砸下去又收我一次费[/quote]<br/>放心吧 第一次摸到不会杀人的 跳完之后看承接的时候才是关键。算了 很难解释", "lou": 1682, "content_length": 73, "reply_to": 863074685, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775013808}, {"pid": 863075922, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 34, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 11:28", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "反正我就想问问 有没有这个区间做 买 这个动作的人  你们直接送我钱就行了  不用过那么多道工序[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 1683, "content_length": 80, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775014092}, {"pid": 863076380, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 11:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863076117,45974302,3245]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=331181]xhox[/uid] (2026-04-01 11:29):[/b]<br/><br/>早上放的量又缩没了[/quote]<br/>下午如果开盘之后15分钟 量能从红转绿 然后突那一下的新高。。。。追进去的人都是菜 肯定有这种人的[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 1684, "content_length": 93, "reply_to": 863076117, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775014245}, {"pid": 863078260, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 25, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 11:42", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863077768,45974302,3246]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=42753091]彦秋Aki[/uid] (2026-04-01 11:39):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大亮个收款码，上午买了航天的已经套了[/quote]<br/><br/>哈哈哈 笑死了", "lou": 1685, "content_length": 17, "from_client": "8 Android", "reply_to": 863077768, "postdatetimestamp": 1775014949}, {"pid": 863086900, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 11, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 12:47", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863086191,45974302,3248]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=38140916]huohuo277[/uid] (2026-04-01 12:41):[/b]<br/><br/>做t接回来算么[s:a2:自戳双目][/quote]<br/>反正我今天不买  我今天减完就看 有什么明天再说<br/>不过我觉得今天倒是没有大跌的可能性 最多有点回撤", "lou": 1686, "content_length": 93, "reply_to": 863086191, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775018869}, {"pid": 863089431, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 13:10", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "早上的港药我觉得可以撤了[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 1687, "content_length": 22, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775020253}, {"pid": 863090235, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 15, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 13:17", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863089911,45974302,3250]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66747163]learla[/uid] (2026-04-01 13:14):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大，鼎龙还要等个小缩量再买吗[s:ac:茶][/quote]<br/>我等明后天找机会 我不会在大盘这个位置买的", "lou": 1688, "content_length": 45, "reply_to": 863089911, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775020648}, {"pid": 863091806, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 8, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 13:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "开始用券商补量了", "lou": 1689, "content_length": 16, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775021447}, {"pid": 863094572, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 14, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 13:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863093882,45974302,3255]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39053967]心情的情[/uid] (2026-04-01 13:48):[/b]<br/><br/>想请教一下早上披萨开板切赵姨的逻辑，是因为赵姨最近调整太多了吗，我早上看指数高开+离3950很近，所以披萨开板了就把赵姨也一起卖了些，想等这波兑现结束后再接，不知道哪里错了[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>模组换原厂啊", "lou": 1690, "content_length": 17, "reply_to": 863093882, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775022846}, {"pid": 863095318, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 27, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 14:00", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863095075,45974302,3256]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64973700]SpamSender[/uid] (2026-04-01 13:58):[/b]<br/><br/>一点半那个位置就是狼大说的突的新高吧[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>之前是不是没有见过这种预判", "lou": 1691, "content_length": 31, "reply_to": 863095075, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775023218}, {"pid": 863095701, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 16, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 14:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们注意看  金银油都跳了  全市场都在谨慎对待明天早上9点的川普讲话", "lou": 1692, "content_length": 61, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775023399}, {"pid": 863095750, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 28, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 14:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863095344,45974302,3256]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64067963]lf1637[/uid] (2026-04-01 14:00):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大请问通宇今天走掉了吗？感觉有点出货走势了[/quote]<br/>。。。。。。。。。。你有病啊 这个位置出货。。。", "lou": 1693, "content_length": 51, "reply_to": 863095344, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775023423}, {"pid": 863096430, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 33, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 14:09", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863096188,45974302,3257]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60916468]灰兔尾[/uid] (2026-04-01 14:07):[/b]<br/><br/>今天红盘大家都很开心，不过我提醒一下，现在虽然各方发言都是一片taco的安静祥和(其实我觉得他们的发言没什么转折，更有可能是缅纳主力超跌自救的资金行为)，但是美国在中东方向的军事资产募集动作是一直不停的，仓位控制及配置上要防御地面登录的可能性，一旦疯王赌了，会产生情绪上的巨大打击和更多的不确定性，调兵遣将是要吞钱的，美军是在团建春游的可能性不大[/quote]<br/>调兵是为了谈判筹码  还有大概5-10天 中东产油国连桶都没了  就要开始大面积停产。这就是重点了", "lou": 1694, "content_length": 89, "reply_to": 863096188, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775023757}, {"pid": 863096933, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 51, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 14:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "你们想知道为什么我早上就能判断下午不会直接跳水下去吗[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 1695, "content_length": 50, "14": {"13": 3}, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775023989}, {"pid": 863097878, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 58, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 14:20", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "因为太明显了 这里市场里面的老油条都是等卖，新丁也不太敢这里追，早上我一看缩量那么慢就知道了 如果快速缩量1000E以上那才有问题<br/>因为没人追，所以就下不来，已知这里就是做局自救，没人高位来追，他自救出不去。那就稳到你忍不住去追，或者更大的资金或者消息做反转。<br/>反正这里就是拼耐性。", "lou": 1696, "content_length": 269, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775024414}, {"pid": 863098325, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 31, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 14:23", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "尾盘会换成金融类的没人的地方去稳 如果只看指数会以为转强了  等下你们看看我说的对不对就行了", "lou": 1697, "content_length": 86, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775024597}, {"pid": 863098668, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 21, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 14:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=863098276,45974302,3259]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=39810331]a471428019[/uid] (2026-04-01 14:22):[/b]<br/><br/>狼大请问既然看好明早川普taco，为什么今天不补回[/quote]<br/>因为他嘴上TACO 但是实际目的还没完全达到 手上动作不会停的 <br/>对于川普 你不要看他说什么 要看他想做什么结果", "lou": 1698, "content_length": 101, "reply_to": 863098276, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775024746}, {"pid": 863099318, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 35, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-01 14:30", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "给你们个贴士 可能有点点机会<br/>